d":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:20:19.000Z","msg":"打死都唔認"},{"pid":"a5d8b7708257cd0454167875e57fcd34cb85cd49","tid":2218377,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"辯方續指，被告於前日中午在律師的陪同下錄取了一份會面記錄，當中保持沉默，之後律師叮囑警方若果被告轉往另一警署或需要再錄取口供時，必定要通知律師。律師亦多次主動聯絡警方，惟警方則回應，會詢問被告是否需要律師，有需要才會作通知。律師亦曾聯絡上警務處一名女副處長，對方當時客氣地回應，如果有需要就會聯絡律師。直至得悉被告進行了第二次的會面記錄後，律師才發現沒有被通知，更遑論警方有詢問過被告。辯方直指警方國安署失職，明言會去信警方要求披露錄影會面前後的資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077709&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu2ztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=5db76fe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077709&h=4bb9689b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077709</a>"},{"pid":"0186be4da04e2d073efe65f2857e469761573d06","tid":2218377,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d00d0c05240b0e856c3551c89d20c48e4ab9cc75","tid":2218377,"uid":142954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"9d0d375f6f172d02b81db75a8055d90afa149dbd","tid":2218377,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63ac70fab9ca03977134591b8b04f5e390e996e5","tid":2218377,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b02f3ab3455cc8f429ef07ee781bdc0e59927cb","tid":2218377,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl